dc_description_s: Includes street index and inset of the Nora area (scale approximately 1:39,000). On verso: map of 'Marion County, Indiana' with indexes to streets and roads, towns and communities, townships, parks, golf and country clubs, and miscellaneous locations; Cram's map of the central business district of Indianapolis showing hotels, theatres, office buildings, etc. (scale approximately 1:9,000); location and distance map; and ill. Scale approximately 1:28,000. Compiled, engraved, printed and published by the George F. Cram Company, Inc.
